<!-- SN02v0 -->
<nav class="sn02 sn02v0 ws-sticky" data-trackas="sn02" data-ocomid="sn02" role="navigation" aria-label="Main Navigation">
<ul class="sn02nav-list cwidth">
<li><a href="#industryspotlight" data-lbl="industryspotlight-anchor">Industry Spotlight</a></li>
<li><a href="#solutions" data-lbl="solutions-anchor">Solutions</a></li>
<li><a href="#sectors" data-lbl=sectors-anchor">Sectors</a></li>
<li><a href="#customers" data-lbl="customers-anchor">Customers</a></li>
<li><a href="#resources" data-lbl="resources-anchor">Resources</a></li>
<li><a href="#getstarted" data-lbl="getstarted-anchor">Get Started</a></li>
<li class="sn02more-menu">
<button aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="sn02more-menu-list" aria-label="View More Options">
<span>View More</span>
</button>
<ul id="sn02more-menu-list" class="sn02more-menu-list" aria-hidden="true"></ul>
</li>
</ul>
</nav>
<!-- /SN02v0 -->
<!-- END: oWidget_C/_Raw-Text/Display -->
<!-- Dispatcher:null default -->
<!-- widgetType: _Raw-Text -->
<!-- SUBTYPETEMPLATE: _Raw-Text/Display -->
<!-- BEGIN: oWidget_C/_Raw-Text/Display replaceOCOM: null -->
<!-- SC04v1 -->
<section class="sc04 sc04v1 cpad" data-trackas="sc04" data-ocomid="sc04">
<div class="sc04w1 cwidth">
<div class="ctitle">
<header>
<h2 id="industryspotlight">Oracle Retail industry spotlight</h2>
</header>
</div>
<ul class="sc04cards cgrid col3 cta-bottom" aria-labelledby="label10">
<li class="sc04card citem mode-light">
<h3 class="hdg-xsm">Ready to unlock faster, data-driven insights?</h3>
<p>Discover lessons from Kroger's retail transformation that you can apply to your own journey.</p>
<div class="cta">
<a class="obttn2" href="https://go.oracle.com/LP=152883?elqCampaignId=664247" target="_blank" data-cxdtrack=":ow:o:h:feb:::" data-adbtrack="CORP260326P00047:ow:o:h:feb:::" data-lbl="kroger-operations-webinar-ctabttn">Access the webinar</a>
</div>
</li>
<li class="sc04card citem mode-light">
<h3 class="hdg-xsm">Oracle named a Leader</h3>
<p>Learn why Oracle was named a Leader in the IDC MarketScape Worldwide Retail AI-Driven Assortment Planning Solutions 2025 Vendor Assessment.</p>
<div class="cta">
<button class="obttn2 lightbox" data-target="/retail/idc-marketscape-worldwide-retail-assortment-planing-solutions-form/" title="Oracle named a Leader" data-lbl="lightbox-open-oracle-named-leader-ctabttn" data-trackas="sc04-lightbox">Access the report</button>
</div>
</li>
<li class="sc04card citem mode-light">
<h3 class="hdg-xsm">Five questions for retail leaders</h3>
<p>To stay ahead, leading retailers must be agile. Consider these five questions to drive resilience in your organization.</p>
<div class="cta">
<a class="obttn2" href="/a/ocom/docs/industries/retail/retail-5-questions-leaders-ask.pdf" target="_blank" data-lbl="retail-5-questions-leaders-ask-ctabttn">See the questions (PDF)</a>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<!-- /SC04v1 -->
<!-- END: oWidget_C/_Raw-Text/Display -->
<!-- Dispatcher:null default -->
<!-- widgetType: _Raw-Text -->
<!-- SUBTYPETEMPLATE: _Raw-Text/Display -->
<!-- BEGIN: oWidget_C/_Raw-Text/Display replaceOCOM: null -->
<!-- SC20v0 -->
<section class="sc20 sc20v0 cpad mode-light bg-texture-4" data-ocomid="sc20" data-trackas="sc20" data-closetxt="Close Panel">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="ctitle">
<header>
<h2 id="solutions">Change how your customers experience retail</h2>
</header>
</div>
<div class="cgrid sc20-panels sc20-close-all" aria-labelledby="sc20-ttl-1">
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="omnichannel-panel">
<ws-icon ico="store"></ws-icon>
<h3>Stores and omnichannel</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="omnichannel-panel">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Xstore Point of Service</h5>
<p>Give your store associates a deeper understanding of customers and greater visibility with robust point-of-service (POS) functionality.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p1" data-lbl="xstore-xlnk">Explore Xstore point of service</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Payment</h5>
<p>Provide a fixed rate and competitive pricing model that enables retailers to anticipate exactly how much they’ll pay for each transaction—regardless of the payment method. There are no additional service or convenience fees or monthly minimums.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p7" data-lbl="payment-xlnk">Explore payment</a></p>
<br />
<h5>CX Commerce</h5>
<p>Provide a frictionless customer experience while boosting conversion rates with integrated POS and ecommerce systems.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p5" data-lbl="cx-commerce-xlnk">Explore CX commerce</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Customer Engagement</h5>
<p>Craft meaningful physical and digital shopping experiences with a real-time view of your customers’ actions and needs at every step of their journey.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p2" data-lbl="customer-engagement-xlnk">Explore customer engagement</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Order Management Suite</h5>
<p>Deliver exceptional customer service while maintaining visibility into order shipments and status. Empower associates with customer appeasement capabilities before and after the sale.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p3" data-lbl="order-management-suite-xlnk">Explore order management suite</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Store Inventory Operations Cloud</h5>
<p>Instantly access accurate inventory data to execute efficient and consistent in-store processes and procedures.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p4" data-lbl="store-inventory-xlnk">Explore store inventory operations cloud</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Collect and Receive</h5>
<p>Gain agility by moving and placing assets, including customers, inventory, and fixtures, across the last mile of the estate that's closest to the point of purchase.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p6" data-lbl="collect-receive-xlnk">Explore collect and receive</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Resources</h5>
<ul class="nobullets">
<li><a href="/retail/idc-marketscape-worldwide-retail-crm-software-form/" role="button" rel="lightbox" data-width="640" title="Oracle named a Leader" data-lbl="lightbox-open-oracle-named-leader-xlnk-lightbox-open-lightbox-open" data-trackas="lightbox">IDC MarketScape: Worldwide Retail Customer Relationship Management Software 2024 Vendor Assessment</a></li>
<li><a href="/a/ocom/docs/industries/retail/3-reasons-retail-store-inventory-operations-cloud.pdf" target="_blank" data-lbl="3-reasons-retail-store-inventory-operations-cloud-xlnk">3 Reasons to Move Retail Store Inventory Operations to the Cloud (PDF)</a></li>
<li><a href="/a/ocom/docs/industries/retail/xstore-point-of-service.pdf" target="_blank" data-lbl="xstore-point-of-service-ds-xlnk">Datasheet: Xstore Point of Service (PDF)</a></li>
<li><a href="https://go.oracle.com/CrossTalk2023#createflexiblestore" data-lbl="flexible-store-layout-xlnk" target="_blank">Video: Create an Agile, Flexible Store Layout</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- /SC01v2 -->
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="pos-hardware-panel">
<ws-icon ico="calculator"></ws-icon>
<h3>POS hardware systems</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="pos-hardware-panel">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>MICROS Workstation 8 Series</h5>
<p>Featuring a slim, 14-inch touch screen display and warm platinum finish, Oracle MICROS Workstation 8 Series fuses a modern, sophisticated look with reliability and dependability.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/pos-systems/#rc30p1" data-lbl="micros-workstation-8-xlnk">Explore MICROS Workstation 8 Series</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Xstore Point of Service</h5>
<p>Give your store associates a deeper understanding of customers and greater visibility with robust POS functionality.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/pos-systems/#rc30p5" data-lbl="micros-workstation-6-xlnk">Explore Xstore point of service</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>MICROS Workstation 6 Series</h5>
<p>The retail environment is demanding, and you need a POS system with modern features that can withstand hard day-to-day use.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/pos-systems/#rc30p2" data-lbl="micros-workstation-6-xlnk">Explore MICROS Workstation 6 Series</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Resources</h5>
<ws-video thumbnail="true" videoid="OpUM6IlVWjw" aria="Introducing Oracle MICROS Workstation 8: Low Profile" data-lbl="yt-OpUM6IlVWjw"></ws-video>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- /SC01v2 -->
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="marketing">
<ws-icon ico="tag"></ws-icon>
<h3>Marketing solutions</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="marketing">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Consumer Insights</h5>
<p>Get customer-specific insights derived from analysis of segmentation, demographics, market basket, product affinity, and promotion performance to design marketing programs that convert to transactions.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/#rc30p3" data-lbl="consumer-insights-xlnk">Explore consumer insights</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Content Management</h5>
<p>Create and deliver personalized content using the power of AI across all applications and marketing, commerce, and customer service channels.</p>
<p><a href="/content-management/" data-lbl="content-management-xlnk">Explore content management</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Customer Loyalty</h5>
<p>Build relationships with your largest and most valuable customers through targeted loyalty and reward programs. Integrate your loyalty program across your entire ecosystem to deliver personalized experiences at every touchpoint.</p>
<p><a href="/cx/marketing/customer-loyalty/retail/" data-lbl="customer-loyalty-xlnk">Explore customer loyalty</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Campaign Management</h5>
<p>Design, manage, execute, and analyze omnichannel marketing campaigns with targeted, personalized messaging at scale.</p>
<p><a href="/cx/marketing/campaign-management/retail/" data-lbl="campaign-management-xlnk">Explore campaign management</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Infinity Behavioral Intelligence</h5>
<p>Optimize your shoppers’ journey in real time using online behavioral data, applied intelligence, and dynamic recommendations.</p>
<p><a href="/cx/marketing/digital-intelligence/retail/" data-lbl="infinity-behavioral-xlnk">Explore infinity behavioral intelligence</a></p>
