</section>
<!-- /SC01v2 -->
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="planning-pricing">
<ws-icon ico="money-investment"></ws-icon>
<h3>Planning, pricing, and optimization</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="planning-pricing">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Merchandise Financial Planning</h5>
<p>Coordinate plans across multiple teams. Invest in the right inventory using science, actualized weekly sales, location views, and unconstrained forecasts.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/planning-optimization/#rc30p2" data-lbl="merchandise-planning-xlnk">Explore merchandise financial planning</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Assortment Planning</h5>
<p>Define and execute local assortments, improve traffic conversion into higher sales and margins, and increase customer satisfaction. Leverage advanced clustering and size profile optimization to ensure the right mix.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/planning-optimization/#rc30p3" data-lbl="assortment-planning-xlnk">Explore assortment planning</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Data Store</h5>
<p>Oracle Retail Data Store is a low-cost, low-code environment that enables retailers to innovate, take control of their data, and extend the capabilities of their Oracle Retail cloud services.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/planning-optimization/#rc30p6" data-lbl="data-store-xlnk">Explore Data Store</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Category Management</h5>
<p>Consolidate multiple data sources into an easy-to-consume format and gain actionable insights and recommendations to drive targeted customer-centric assortments.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/planning-optimization/#rc30p4" data-lbl="category-management-xlnk">Explore category management</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Science Platform Cloud</h5>
<p>Use our embedded, retail-specific AI and machine learning to improve every aspect of merchandise planning, leveraging customer segment decision trees, demand transference analysis, size profile optimization, space allocation optimization, and planogram performance data.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/" data-lbl="science-platform-xlnk">Explore science platform cloud</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Enterprise Performance Management</h5>
<p>Understand the impact of strategic decisions across your bottom line, balance sheet, cash flow, and shareholder value before including them in your operational plan.</p>
<p><a href="/performance-management/" data-lbl="enterprise-performance-management-xlnk">Explore enterprise performance management</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Assortment and Space Optimization</h5>
<p>Optimize assortments to available space to maximize planogram performance, return on space, sales, revenue, and profits.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/planning-optimization/#rc30p5" data-lbl="assortment-space-xlnk">Explore assortment and space optimization</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Resources</h5>
<ul class="nobullets">
<li><a href="/retail/assortment-planning/" data-lbl="assortment-planning-xlnk">Article: What Is Assortment Planning in Retail? 9 Ways to Optimize</a></li>
<li><a href="https://go.oracle.com/CrossTalk2023#hibbettretail" data-lbl="hibbettretail-xlnk" target="_blank">Video: Hibbett Retail: A Connected View of Inventory Planning</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- /SC01v2 -->
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="merchandise-operations">
<ws-icon ico="money-analytics"></ws-icon>
<h3>Merchandise operations management</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="merchandise-operations">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Merchandising System</h5>
<p>Manage, control, and perform seamless execution of day-to-day merchandising activities, including purchasing, distribution, order fulfillment, and financial close.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p1" data-lbl="merchandising-system-xlnk">Explore merchandising system</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Invoice Matching</h5>
<p>Manage the matching, reconciliation, and payment of supplier invoices with a configurable, automated solution. Resolve identified exceptions using workflows that are aligned with business policies.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p2" data-lbl="invoice-matching-xlnk">Explore invoice matching</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Sales Audit</h5>
<p>Process and validate sales transactions from all channels. Ensure clean and consistent sales information while managing discrepancies by exception.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p1" data-lbl="sales-audit-xlnk">Explore sales audit</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Retail Pricing</h5>
<p>Implement a complete, rules-based pricing engine that supports regular, promotional, and clearance pricing across all touchpoints.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p4" data-lbl="price-management-xlnk">Explore retail pricing</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Allocation</h5>
<p>Deliver products to the right place at the right time with a powerful, accurate, and easy-to-use method of allocating merchandise. Effectively allocate products through their lifecycle to get them in front of the right shoppers.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p3" data-lbl="allocation-xlnk">Explore allocation</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Supplier Evaluation</h5>
<p>Evaluate merchandising suppliers and enable the assessment and governance of ethical, environmental, safety, and quality performance to protect your brand from supply chain risks and improve sustainability.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p6" data-lbl="supplier-evaluation-xlnk">Explore supplier evaluation</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Store Inventory Operations Cloud</h5>
<p>Access accurate store-stock data to execute seamless commerce anywhere through consistent, efficient, and effective in-store processes and procedures.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/omnichannel/#rc30p4" data-lbl="store-inventory-operations-xlnk">Explore store inventory operations cloud</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Merchandising Insights</h5>
<p>Identify actionable merchandising opportunities across touchpoints, including back orders and returns, top/bottom sellers, demand, fulfillment, and price and promotion analysis.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p5" data-lbl="merchandising-cloud-xlnk">Explore merchandising insights</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Data Store</h5>
<p>Oracle Retail Data Store is a low-cost, low-code environment that enables retailers to innovate, take control of their data, and extend the capabilities of their Oracle Retail cloud services.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p7" data-lbl="data-store-xlnk">Explore Data Store</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Resources</h5>
<ul class="nobullets">
<li><a href="https://go.oracle.com/CrossTalk2023#abercrombie" data-lbl="abercrombie-xlnk" target="_blank">Video: Abercrombie &amp; Fitch Co.: Zero Downtime on the Path to Innovation</a></li>
<li><a href="https://go.oracle.com/CrossTalk2023#flink" data-lbl="crosstalk2023-xlnk" target="_blank">Video: Flink: Online Grocery Takes the Fast Lane to Digital Transformation</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- /SC01v2 -->
<button class="sc20-bttn cgrid-3" aria-controls="scm">
<ws-icon ico="inventory-cost-revaluation"></ws-icon>
<h3>Supply chain management</h3>
</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="scm">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Demand Forecasting</h5>
<p>Maximize forecast accuracy for the entire product lifecycle with next-generation retail science paired with exception-driven processes and delivered on our platform for modern retailing.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/supply-chain/#rc30p1" data-lbl="demand-forecasting-xlnk">Explore demand forecasting</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Inventory Planning Optimization Cloud</h5>
<p>Get better visibility into supply chains and leverage AI and machine learning to manage inventory levels, improve demand forecasting, identify risks, and provide recommendations to guard against inventory shortages or delays.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/supply-chain/#rc30p3" data-lbl="store-inventory-xlnk">Explore inventory planning optimization cloud</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Inventory Optimization Cloud</h5>
<p>Instantly access accurate store-stock data to execute consistent, efficient, and effective in-store processes and procedures.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/supply-chain/#rc30p2" data-lbl="inventory-optimization-xlnk">Explore inventory optimization cloud</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Allocation</h5>
<p>Deliver products to the right place at the right time with a powerful, accurate, and easy-to-use method of allocating merchandise. Effectively allocate products through their lifecycle to get them in front of the right shoppers.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p3" data-lbl="allocation-xlnk">Explore allocation</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Logistics</h5>
<p>Seamlessly manage transportation, global trade, and distribution to maximize order fulfillment and minimize logistics costs while adapting to business disruptions and changes in your supply chain.</p>
<p><a href="/scm/logistics/" data-lbl="logistic-xlnk">Explore logistics</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Warehouse Management</h5>
<p>Manage and optimize essential supply chain processes for omnichannel fulfillment, with complete visibility and control of orders and inventory throughout the distribution process.</p>
<p><a href="/scm/logistics/warehouse-management/" data-lbl="warehouse-management-xlnk">Explore warehouse management</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Supply Chain Collaboration</h5>
<p>Streamline collaboration between retailers and suppliers, simplifying the management and analysis of critical supply chain information. This helps lead to more efficient and effective merchandising strategies.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/supply-chain/#rc30p7" data-lbl="supply-chain-xlnk">Explore supply chain collaboration</a></p>
<h5>Resources</h5>
<ul class="nobullets">
<li><a href="/retail/fashion/fashion-supply-chain/" data-lbl="fashion-supply-chain-xlnk">Article: Fashion Supply Chain: Everything You Need to Know</a></li>
<li><a href="/retail/3-steps-to-simplifying-demand-forecasting-for-fashion/" data-lbl="3-steps-to-simplifying-demand-forecasting-for-fashion-xlnk">Report: 3 Steps to Simplifying Demand Forecasting for Fashion Retailers</a></li>
<li><ws-video thumbnail="true" videoid="ZUUAu1mN2WE" aria="The Platform for Modern Retail Inventory Management" data-lbl="yt-ZUUAu1mN2WE"></ws-video></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
