</button>
<!-- SC01v2 -->
<section class="sc01 sc01v2 panelcontent cpad" data-ocomid="sc01" id="ai">
<div class="cwidth">
<div class="sc01-3col">
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Inventory Planning Optimization Cloud</h5>
<p>Get better visibility into supply chains and leverage AI and machine learning to manage inventory levels, improve demand forecasting, identify risks, and provide recommendations to guard against inventory shortages or delays.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/#rc30p4" data-lbl="inventory-optimization-xlnk">Explore inventory planning optimization cloud</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Merchandising Insights</h5>
<p>Identify actionable merchandising opportunities across touchpoints, including back orders and returns, top/bottom sellers, demand, fulfillment, and price and promotion analysis.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/merchandising/cloud/#rc30p5" data-lbl="merchandising-insights-xlnk">Explore merchandising insights</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Lifecycle Pricing Optimization Cloud</h5>
<p>Analytical insights provide recommendations for optimal promotions, markdowns, and targeted offers that maximize profits and sell-through.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/#rc30p2" data-lbl="lifecycle-optimization-cloud-xlnk">Explore lifecycle pricing optimization cloud</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Consumer Insights Cloud</h5>
<p>Get customer-specific insights derived from analysis of segmentation, demographics, market basket, product affinity, and promotion performance to design marketing programs that convert to transactions.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/#rc30p3" data-lbl="consumer-insights-cloud-xlnk">Explore consumer insights cloud</a></p>
<br />
<h5>Assortment and Space Optimization</h5>
<p>Optimize assortments to available space for each store to maximize planogram performance, return on space, sales, revenue, and profits while improving customer satisfaction.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/#rc30p5" data-lbl="assortment-space-xlnk">Explore assortment and space optimization</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sc01-citem">
<h5>Science Platform Cloud</h5>
<p>Use embedded, retail-specific AI and machine learning to improve every aspect of merchandise planning, leveraging customer segment decision trees, demand transference analysis, size profile optimization, space allocation optimization, and planogram performance data.</p>
<p><a href="/retail/ai-analytics/" data-lbl="science-platform-cloud-xlnk">Explore science platform cloud</a></p>
